+                return splits
+
+
+val_percent_check
+^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
+
+How much of validation dataset to check.
+Useful when debugging or testing something that happens at the end of an epoch.
+
+Example::
+
+    # default used by the Trainer
+    trainer = Trainer(val_percent_check=1.0)
+
